diagnosis Similar in various traits to 
<taxonomicName LSID-HNS="urn:lsid:biosci.ohio-state.edu:osuc_concepts:181839" class="Insecta" family="Formicidae" genus="Pheidole" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Pheidole angulifera Wilson" lsidName-HNS="Pheidole angulifera Wilson" order="Hymenoptera" pageNumber="534" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="angulifera">angulifera</taxonomicName>
, 
